reviews.review_text:
SWEET These tapes rock, Charlie Connor. You're my new hero for listening.
I'm still looking for the NYE show (mid 80's) where Ken Kesey sang "Gather at the river" . My cassette was lost years ago and no one even knows what I'm talking about. I got all the Dead , I want the Kesey.
